Big Brother Naija, BBNaija, housemate, Tolanibaj, on Tuesday said she was warned against having sex on the reality television show. Tolanibaj disclosed that her friends warned her against engaging in sexual intercourse throughout her stay on the show. The BBNaija housemate disclosed this to fellow housemate, Prince during a conversation. Against the backdrop of the advice, Tolanibaj said she has no plans of having sex on national television. “I’m not having sex on TV, please. “My friends already warned me. I’m not that crazy because I’m American I will do shit like that”.